'''Void Essence''' is a [[Monster Loot]] item which can drop from [[Shadow Brute]]s, [[Shadow Shaman]]s, [[Shadow Sniper]]s, [[Haunted Skull]]s, [[Serpent]]s and [[Spider]]s. [[Krobus]] also sells 10 a day for {{price|100}}.  A [[Void Salmon]] [[Fish Pond]] may produce 5-10 Void Essence when the population of the pond reaches 8.

The [[Void Ghost Pendant]] can be purchased from the [[Desert Trader]] in exchange for 200 Void Essence, once the player has reached 10 hearts of [[friendship]] with [[Krobus]].

